dt: {bc}any of a genus ({it}Laminaria{/it}) of large chiefly perennial kelps with an unbranched cylindrical or flattened stipe and a smooth or convoluted blade

shortdef: any of a genus (Laminaria) of large chiefly perennial kelps with an unbranched cylindrical or flattened stipe and a smooth or convoluted blade; broadly : any of various related kelps (order Laminariales)
